{"title":"赠曹禺","authors":["茅盾"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠曹禺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅盾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年海上惊雷雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾散云开明朗天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阅尽风霜君更健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昭君今继越王篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年代末，《雷雨》在上海演出，震惊剧坛。《明朗的天》为曹禺同志在解放后所写第一个话剧，《胆剑篇》是他所写的第一个历史剧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作者附注"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}